headline: Norfolk Southern to present at J.P. Morgan Industrials Conference
summary: Norfolk Southern Corporation (NYSE: NSC) Executive Vice President and Chief Operating Officer John Orr and Executive Vice President and Chief Financial Officer Jason Zampi will participate in a fireside chat at the 2025 J.P. Morgan Industrials Conference. Details on listening to the discussion follow below.

headline: 3 Railroad Stocks to Watch From a Challenging Industry
summary: Shareholder-friendly initiatives bode well for the Zacks Transportation-Railroad industry. UNP, CP and NSC are well-poised to capitalize on the bullishness.
